<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1281 gunēṁṭi vaiśākha vimala tṛ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tīyayu sōmavāramunāṁḍu matsyakulasaṁjātuṁḍaina pā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>lakoṁḍa kaṟṟijīyana tanaku nāyurārōgyaiśvaryyābhivṛ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhanāthuni saṁnnidhini nityamunnu O
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ka Akhaṁḍadīpamu veluṁguṭaku sūrebōyuni koḍu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ku Eṟyabōyuni vaśamunaṁ beṭina mōdālu Ēṁbha
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> lekka mōdālu 50 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dīpapratima Okaṁḍukunnu E
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṛyabōyuṁḍu māsapaḍi neyi decci bhaṁḍārāmaṁdu pra
<lb n="9" break="no"/>vēśamu cēyaṁgalāṁḍu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmmu Ācaṁdrārkasthāyi
<lb n="10" break="no"/>gāṁ jallaṁgaladu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatruṇāpi kṛtō dharmma<unclear>ḥ</unclear> pālanīyō manīṣi
<lb n="11" break="no"/>bhiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatrurēva hi śatru<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> syāddharmmaḥ śatrurnna kasyacit <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī
<lb n="12"/>dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇavula rakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> maṁgaḷamahā śrīśrīśrīśrī 
</p>

